Pre-Game Insights: Angola qualified for the knockout stage for the first time in AFCON history.
Namibia stunned Tunisia by beating them in the tournament's opening match.
Bruno Paz and Fredy will be hoping to recover in time to play an important role in this match.
Miscellaneous Highlights: This match will determine if Angola can qualify for the quarterfinal for the first time in their history.
Deon Hotto has been one of the biggest scorers on the team for Namibia.
Others: Angola are unbeaten in the last eight matches
Namibia have failed to score in the last two matches
Angola head into the round of 16 as unbeaten
